scene_description_enriched: The scene depicts Saint Sebastian, bound to a tree trunk, pierced by arrows. He is shown with a halo, indicating his sainthood. To his left, a man in a red tunic and orange hat draws a bow, aiming an arrow at Sebastian. The background is a lush green landscape with trees and foliage under a blue sky. This imagery represents the martyrdom of Saint Sebastian, a Roman soldier who was condemned to death by Emperor Diocletian and shot with arrows.
